{"tid":1309743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂牆起源 咪撕走人地意見","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:07:46.000Z","uid":42246,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f26cc20d3ea986c3b986f4664da1db204c00f6b","tid":1309743,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"連儂牆原址位於捷克布拉格，因1988年群眾不滿胡薩克共產主義政權，在布拉格修道院大廣場的一面牆寫上反抗標語，當中包括傳奇樂隊Beatles的靈魂人物John Lennon的肖像及歌詞，因為John Lennon自80年代起，被視為反戰、追求和平的重要文化象徵符號。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的，是John Lennon在1980年12月8日於紐約公寓遭瘋狂歌迷槍殺，故他沒有到過連儂牆，但群眾將他的精神以塗鴉、文字，甚至街頭演唱的形式延續下去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆有一個不明文規定，就是有顏料在手，就可以不必管前者的塗鴉畫上創作，所以連儂牆的模樣不停在轉變，唯一不變的就是和平、反戰的信息一直都在。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪撕走 但可以cover 每個人都可以發聲<br />\n新一浪聲音蓋過原有聲音<br />\n你想堅持自己聲音 就再蓋過新既聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a536952fbbd4b8868e27535c8a0b5722445f3b","tid":1309743,"uid":95520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"絕對唔係撕走喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c08dbe00c6da9a9075150bae2de4c3a2db92bb","tid":1309743,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31a536952fbbd4b8868e27535c8a0b5722445f3b","tid":1309743,"uid":95520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"絕對唔係撕走喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"我叫人咪撕走姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7300234cae654e263a51bb19257c7422eb8e328e","tid":1309743,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40ed28d85a2e5c1c8a9431fc654dd0a6a0f710d7","tid":1309743,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c